&lt;div class="prompt input_prompt"&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="inner_cell"&gt;
&lt;div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html"&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;On the Eve of Nelson Mandela Day&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collaboration by:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ADHT,  Bermuda College, Chewstick, HRC, Imagine Bermuda&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Presents&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Another Kind of ‘Happy Hour’&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Based @ the Bermuda College Library&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;FRIDAY, JULY 17TH 5.30 – 7.30 pm&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MUSIC……….POETRY………STORY-SHARING&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NETWORKING…….NETPLAYING&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Meet and Greet,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Even stump your feet,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although Challenging,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remember, Life is Sweet!&lt;/p&gt;
