&lt;p&gt;There are others planning events, I will try to post details here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I am thinking of going to different events and doing &lt;em&gt;sixty-seven minutes of pi&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

