&lt;p&gt;Mandela often spoke of Ubuntu:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ubuntu does not mean that people should not enrich themselves. The
question therefore is: Are you going to do so in order to enable the
community around you to be able to improve?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

