&lt;div class="inner_cell"&gt;
&lt;div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html"&gt;
&lt;h2 id="Sixty-seven-minutes-of-$\pi$"&gt;Sixty-seven minutes of $\pi$&lt;a class="anchor-link" href="http://openbermuda.github.io/80days/posts/sixty-seven-minutes.html#Sixty-seven-minutes-of-%24%5Cpi%24"&gt;¶&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Angles are measured in different units.  Mostly, people seem to use degrees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A right angle is 90 degrees.  The angles in a triangle add up to 180 degrees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In mathematics it is often useful to use different units, &lt;em&gt;radians&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$\pi$ radians is equal to 180 degrees.  So the angles in a triangle
add up to 180 degrees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now just as there are 60 minutes in an hour, there are also 60 minutes in a degree.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So, 67 minutes of $\pi$ is just 67 minutes from 180 degrees.&lt;/p&gt;
$$ x = \pi * 67 / (180 * 60)$$
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="cell border-box-sizing code_cell rendered"&gt;
&lt;div class="input"&gt;
&lt;div class="prompt input_prompt"&gt;In [10]:&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="inner_cell"&gt;
    &lt;div class="input_area"&gt;
&lt;div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# In python&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;math&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;pi&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;67&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;180&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;60&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="output_wrapper"&gt;
&lt;div class="output"&gt;


&lt;div class="output_area"&gt;&lt;div class="prompt output_prompt"&gt;Out[10]:&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;div class="output_text output_subarea output_execute_result"&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;0.019489509980603347&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="cell border-box-sizing code_cell rendered"&gt;
&lt;div class="input"&gt;
&lt;div class="prompt input_prompt"&gt;In [11]:&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="inner_cell"&gt;
    &lt;div class="input_area"&gt;
&lt;div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# Now 67 minutes of pi number begins 0.01948.&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="mi"&gt;1948&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;67&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
