&lt;pre&gt;2015&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"&gt;
&lt;div class="prompt input_prompt"&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="inner_cell"&gt;
&lt;div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So if Mandela had started his campaigning on his birthday in 1948 he would still be at it today.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The UN are just asking you to spend 67 minutes helping others on his birthday.&lt;/p&gt;

